<db:section xml:id="position-prop">
<db:title>[read-only] position : real</db:title>
<db:para>This property holds the logical position of the handle.</db:para>
<db:para>The position is expressed as a fraction of the control's size, in the range <db:code>0.0 - 1.0</db:code>. For visualizing a slider, the right-to-left aware <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-controls-slider.xml#visualPosition-prop">visualPosition</db:link> should be used instead.</db:para>
